  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Site Engineer",
  "description": "<h3>Job Description:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Site project management</li>\n  <li>To carry out coordination and liaisons with all relevant parties.</li>\n  <li>Conduct project site inspection.</li>\n  <li>Assist project head to co-ordinate &amp; carry out all works assigned.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for assessing progress claims and reporting to management.</li>\n  <li>Check and monitor work and site progress according to schedules.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with the main contractor, consultants, sub-contractors, and suppliers.</li>\n  <li>Plan and advise the construction foreman on sequencing and arrangement of work.</li>\n  <li>Need to communicate with workers regarding project progress.</li>\n  <li>Handle inspection-related works.</li>\n  <li>And handle any other ad-hoc duties and tasks assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>Requirements:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferably at least 4 years relevant experience in the related field for this position</li>\n  <li>Be able to work independently with minimum guidance</li>\n  <li>Good team player, with a keen desire to learn, contribute, advance, and progress with the company.</li>\n</ul>",
